<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - sybk mn kl ạlly fạt, yạmạ jwạnạ ḥkạyạt lw hnḥky f ạldẖkryạt, yạmạ ạljrạḥ sạbt ʿlạmạt
 1- yạmạ bạkynạ ʿạl rạḥ, yạmạ ʿạlynạ ṣwtnạ nwạḥ
 yạmạ ktyr ḍạʿ mʿ ạlryạḥ, lạ sẖfnạ nwr wlạ sẖfnạ ṣbạḥ lkn hw wlạ ywm sạbny, ṭwl ḥyạty wạqf jnby lyh ạ̉fkr wạ̉sẖgẖl bạly, ạnạ yswʿy hw ậmạly
 2- yạmạ sẖqy
 t
 ạ̉yạm w lyạly wṣḥyḥ ạldnyạ mlhạsẖ gẖạly
 ạsẖky lmyn wạḥky lmyn gẖyrh , hw ạlhy wdạry bḥạly̱
 kl dqyqh fyhạ sẖạylny wkl mạ ạqlq byṭmny
 ạṣl ạnạ ạbnh, wạ̉kẖd bạlh mny wạ̹yh fy bkrh hykẖwfny</lyrics>
<title>sybk mn kl ạlly fạt</title>
